sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as API Client
    participant GW as vllm-orchestrator-gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orch as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant Det as Content Detectors<br/>(e.g., regex-detector)
    participant LLM as vLLM Model Server

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Content Detection

    Client->>GW: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token><br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>stream: false
    Note over GW: Route dispatcher matches route_name<br/>Injects detector config from YAML<br/>(detectors, params, type: input/output)
    GW->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token> (forwarded)<br/>x-forwarded-* headers forwarded<br/>Optional mTLS client cert (PKCS#12)
    Orch->>Det: Run input detectors
    Det-->>Orch: Input detection results
    Orch->>LLM: Forward to model (if input passes)
    LLM-->>Orch: Chat completion response
    Orch->>Det: Run output detectors
    Det-->>Orch: Output detection results
    Orch-->>GW: JSON response with detections
    Note over GW: check_payload_detections():<br/>If detections found AND fallback configured,<br/>replace response content with fallback message
    GW-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original or fallback)

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Content Detection (SSE)

    Client->>GW: POST /{route_name}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer <token><br/>stream: true
    Note over GW: Route dispatcher matches route_name<br/>Injects detector config
    GW->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>stream: true<br/>Optional mTLS
    Orch->>Det: Run input detectors
    Det-->>Orch: Input detection results

    loop SSE Stream (chunk by chunk)
        Orch->>LLM: Stream inference request
        LLM-->>Orch: SSE chunk
        Orch->>Det: Run output detector on chunk
        Det-->>Orch: Chunk detection result
        Orch-->>GW: data: {chunk JSON with detections}
        Note over GW: Parse SSE data: line<br/>Deserialize chunk<br/>Apply per-chunk fallback if detections
        GW-->>Client: data: {chunk JSON}<br/>(original or fallback per-chunk)
    end

    Orch-->>GW: data: [DONE]
    GW-->>Client: data: [DONE]
